# accepts these types through term_dict (Classify -> NumericI64), but the
# rocksdb row store refuses TIMESTAMPTZ / TIME / TIMESTAMP_MS / TIMESTAMP_NS
# / TIMETZ / TIME_NS payloads. The parquet round-trip preserves the column
# types while bypassing rocksdb -- same shape as m_unsup / g11_a_v.
